{
  "stem": "24242.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you ask me what happened of summer 1942.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Am I correct?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You were still 60 people then?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We're about 50, 60 people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then the only thing was to-- my brothers had arms.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they were the only ones.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The rest of them came out with nothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "War is a problem.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "To hide, there is no problem because the woods are big.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But to get food, you have to go at night to some farmers on good terms, to some on bad.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You can't always come to a-- to five farmers and they should support you constantly.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They don't have-- they're not that wealthy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And particularly to the good friends, to the good farmers that helped us all along and give us information constantly, that our parents were butchered, together with other 5,000 Jews in-- in [INAUDIBLE], you don't want to go to him and ask him for food for 50 people.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Was a-- was a problem simply to feed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Which some older Jews from-- my sister is from Toby's family.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Her father-in-law and her brother-in-laws, made a remark that there was no more, that's even too many already we are.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then, on those words, came out Tuvia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was the first one that said, if there is a Jewish child, if there is a Jewish woman or an old Jew, if he wants to come to us, whatever we will eat, he will have.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And word got around in the ghettos-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] that Tuvia has said that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And this is the way-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] he got very popular among-- among the weaker Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They would not do it or if not him.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
